Stage 2 load shedding will resume at 09:00 on Saturday morning and continue until 22:00, Eskom has said. Eskom had managed to avoid nationwide load shedding during the lockdown, but power cuts recommenced on Friday. Gauteng, meanwhile, has faced bouts of localised rolling blackouts known as "load rotation", which Eskom has attributed to a prevalence of vandalism and illegal connections.   https://www.news24.com/fin24/economy/eskom-load-shedding-is-back-20200710 